          <description><![CDATA[The Chicago Cubs have demoted infield prospect Matt Shaw and relief pitcher Nate Pearson to Triple-A and recalled pitchers Luke Little and Daniel Palencia from the Iowa Cubs, while reinstating Vidal Bruján and moving relief pitcher Eli Morgan to the 15-day IL with a right elbow impingement.]]></description>
